node.text:
@versed is also hosting a contest!

Here’s how it works:
1. Create an impression of what self care looks like to you
2. Post it in-feed on your Instagram or on Tik Tok
3. Use the #SelfCareCheckUp
We will pick 1 winner and 1 runner-up 
- First-place will receive a $500 cash prize and $500 donated to the charity of their choosing 
- Second-place will receive a $200 cash prize and $200 donated to the charity of their choosing
See @versed for full details and T&C.

node.text: It’s been so hard finding the strength to type this. I lost my baby brother. My heart, my soul, my twin, my best friend. Idk how I’m going to go on in this world without you. I really don’t want to live without you. I love you so much baby soooo much. I wish I could wake up from this nightmare. Fly high my king until I see you again. I know the angels will be all on you.🕊💚
